{
  "script_id": "logarithm-spiral",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "logarithm-spiral",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/logarithm-spiral/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.88,
      "size": 30096,
      "text": "鹦鹉螺的壳，向日葵的种子，还有旋涡星系的巨臂。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "logarithm-spiral",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/logarithm-spiral/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.43,
      "size": 38880,
      "text": "它们身上都藏着同一条曲线，越转越大，却始终保持相同的形状。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "logarithm-spiral",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/logarithm-spiral/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.95,
      "size": 31248,
      "text": "这就是对数螺线，一条被大自然反复采用的优美螺线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "logarithm-spiral",
      "section_id": "equation",
      "line_id": "eq-1",
      "filename": "equation-eq-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/logarithm-spiral/xiaoxiao/equation-eq-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.25,
      "size": 36000,
      "text": "在极坐标里，它的方程写作 r 等于 a 乘以 e 的 b 乘 theta 次方。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "logarithm-spiral",
      "section_id": "equation",
      "line_id": "eq-2",
      "filename": "equation-eq-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/logarithm-spiral/xiaoxiao/equation-eq-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.9,
      "size": 30384,
      "text": "theta 是转过的角度，半径 r 随角度呈指数增长。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "logarithm-spiral",
      "section_id": "equation",
      "line_id": "eq-3",
      "filename": "equation-eq-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/logarithm-spiral/xiaoxiao/equation-eq-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 28080,
      "text": "常数 a 定起点大小，常数 b 控制螺线的松紧。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "logarithm-spiral",
      "section_id": "equiangular",
      "line_id": "ang-1",
      "filename": "equiangular-ang-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/logarithm-spiral/xiaoxiao/equiangular-ang-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.49,
      "size": 39888,
      "text": "在螺线的任意一点，切线和从中心引出的径向之间，都夹着同一个角。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "logarithm-spiral",
      "section_id": "equiangular",
      "line_id": "ang-2",
      "filename": "equiangular-ang-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/logarithm-spiral/xiaoxiao/equiangular-ang-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.65,
      "size": 42336,
      "text": "这个定角等于 arctan 一比 b，与你走到哪里无关，所以它又叫等角螺线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "logarithm-spiral",
      "section_id": "selfsimilar",
      "line_id": "self-1",
      "filename": "selfsimilar-self-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/logarithm-spiral/xiaoxiao/selfsimilar-self-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.37,
      "size": 37872,
      "text": "每多转一整圈，半径就放大固定的倍数，等于 e 的 2 pi b 次方。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "logarithm-spiral",
      "section_id": "selfsimilar",
      "line_id": "self-2",
      "filename": "selfsimilar-self-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/logarithm-spiral/xiaoxiao/selfsimilar-self-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.39,
      "size": 38304,
      "text": "于是把螺线放大或缩小，看上去和原来一模一样，这就是自相似。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "logarithm-spiral",
      "section_id": "selfsimilar",
      "line_id": "self-3",
      "filename": "selfsimilar-self-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/logarithm-spiral/xiaoxiao/selfsimilar-self-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.89,
      "size": 46224,
      "text": "相比之下，阿基米德螺线 r 等于 a 加 b theta，半径是线性增长，圈距均匀。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "logarithm-spiral",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/logarithm-spiral/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.81,
      "size": 28944,
      "text": "调整参数 b，看螺线在松散和紧致之间变化。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "logarithm-spiral",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/logarithm-spiral/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.0,
      "size": 31968,
      "text": "再叠加阿基米德螺线做对比，感受指数与线性的不同。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "logarithm-spiral",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/logarithm-spiral/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.25,
      "size": 36000,
      "text": "对数螺线由 r 等于 a e 的 b theta 次方描述，半径指数增长。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "logarithm-spiral",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/logarithm-spiral/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.28,
      "size": 36432,
      "text": "它处处等角，每转一圈按固定倍数放大，因而完美自相似。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "logarithm-spiral",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/logarithm-spiral/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "从贝壳到星系，它把生长的秘密写进螺线，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
